ROCKET PATROL MODIFICATIONS

1.) Implemented a charging mechanic for the cannon. Longer charges increase the speed of the projectile. (20)
2.) Implemented mouse controls and removed keyboard controls for the cannon only. (20)
3.) Added a countdown timer display on the top-right corner of the Play scene. Displays time remaining in game. (10)
4.) Implemented add-time bonus (1 sec.) for every successful hit on enemy spaceships. (20)